Package: optweight
Type: Package
Title: Targeted Stable Balancing Weights Using Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Noah Greifer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Noah Greifer <noah.greifer@gmail.com>
Description: Use optimization to estimate weights that balance covariates for binary, multinomial, continuous, and longitudinal treatments in the spirit of Zubizarreta (2015) <doi:10.1080/01621459.2015.1023805>. The degree of balance can be specified for each covariate.
